OL,3,CZoo unveils plans for 'most
OL,4,Csignificant' redevelopment in 100 years
OL,6,FThe owners of Paignton Zoo have
OL,7,Funveiled plans to transform its site,
OL,8,Fdescribing it as "the most significant
OL,9,Fredevelopment of the site in its 103-
OL,10,Fyear history."
OL,12,FThe Devon-based attraction said it
OL,13,Fhoped the investment would protect the
OL,14,Ffuture of the zoo for years to come.
OL,16,FVisitors will see the return of zebras
OL,17,Fand the arrival of white rhinos as
OL,18,Fpart of the project, which involves
OL,19,Fsplitting the site into four themed
OL,20,Fzones.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
