PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774980701
OL,3,CZoo unveils plans for 'most
OL,4,Csignificant' redevelopment in 100 years
OL,6,F"This is a hugely exciting moment,"
OL,7,Fsaid Steven van den Heuvel, transition
OL,8,Fmanager at Paignton Zoo.
OL,10,F"What we're doing is not just updating
OL,11,Findividual habitats, but re-thinking
OL,12,Fthe entire visitor experience and how
OL,13,Fwe tell the story of the animals in
OL,14,Four care."
OL,16,FThe zoo was taken over by Dutch
OL,17,Fleisure company Libema in December
OL,18,F2025, after it was put on the market
OL,19,Fby the Wild Planet Trust due to rising
OL,20,Foperating costs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
