OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774980701
OL,3,CZoo unveils plans for 'most
OL,4,Csignificant' redevelopment in 100 years
OL,6,FLibema said the first phase of the
OL,7,Ftransformation is underway, with the
OL,8,Fexisting giraffe paddock being
OL,9,Fexpanded into a savannah for giraffes,
OL,10,Fzebras, and ostrich as part of the new
OL,11,F'Grasslands zone'.
OL,13,FPlans are also progressing across the
OL,14,Fnew 'Rainforest zone,' 'Island zone, '
OL,15,Fand 'Wetlands zone,' where a new
OL,16,Fhabitat is being prepared for
OL,17,Fsitatunga, a rare antelope species
OL,18,Fknown for its ability to move through
OL,19,Fwater.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774980701
OL,3,CZoo unveils plans for 'most
OL,4,Csignificant' redevelopment in 100 years
OL,6,FThe zoo said the investment will
OL,7,Fstrengthen its conservation work for
OL,8,Fthe future, and it hopes to welcome
OL,9,Fwhite rhinoceros to the site following
OL,10,Fthe creation of a new Plains habitat.
OL,12,FMr van den Heuvel added: "Grasslands
OL,13,Fis the first major step, but it's part
OL,14,Fof a much bigger transformation
OL,15,Fhappening across the whole site.
OL,17,F"Over time, visitors will see new
OL,18,Fspecies, new habitats, and a
OL,19,Fcompletely new way of exploring the
OL,20,Fzoo.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
