OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1774980701
OL,3,CZoo unveils plans for 'most
OL,4,Csignificant' redevelopment in 100 years
OL,6,F"Importantly, this evolution stays
OL,7,Ftrue to what Paignton Zoo has always
OL,8,Fstood for ` conservation, education,
OL,9,Fand animal welfare remain at the heart
OL,10,Fof everything we do, and this
OL,11,Finvestment allows us to strengthen
OL,12,Fthat work for the future."
OL,14,FCredit: Guy Henderson, Local Democracy
OL,15,FReporting Service
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
